short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Inspect GraphQL requests and response data

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Allows inspecting GraphQL Requests via a devtools panel.
Analyzes network requests for that tab and if it finds the common GraphQL request / response schemas, adds them to the list.

See and contribute under https://github.com/lokmeinmatz/GraphQL-Inspect
v0.1.3
